entry.name: entry
entry.description: Returns the entry of a given binary tree.

is_empty_tree.name: is_empty_tree
is_empty_tree.description: Returns a boolean value, indicating whether the given value is an empty binary tree.

is_tree.name: is_tree
is_tree.description: Returns a boolean value, indicating whether the given value is a binary tree.

left_branch.name: left_branch
left_branch.description: Returns the left branch of a given binary tree.

make_empty_tree.name: make_empty_tree
make_empty_tree.description: Returns an empty binary tree, represented by the empty list null

make_tree.name: make_tree
make_tree.description: Returns a binary tree node composed of the specified left subtree, value and right subtree.

right_branch.name: right_branch
right_branch.description: Returns the right branch of a given binary tree.
